'''厄科号测量舰'''（'''HMS Echo'''）是[[英国皇家海军|英国皇家海军]]委托制造的首批多功能[[水文地理学|水文地理]]测量舰之一。与其姊妹船[[企业号测量舰_(H88)|企业号]]组成[[厄科级测量舰_(2002)|厄科级]]测量舰队。2002年由德云郡的阿普勒多尔造船受托建造<ref name=RN>{{cite web |url= http://www.royal-navy.mod.uk/server/show/nav.00h001001006004001 |title= HMS ''Echo'' at the Royal Navy website |accessdate= 2009-06-20 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080609063812/http://www.royal-navy.mod.uk/server/show/nav.00h001001006004001 |archivedate= 2008-06-09 }}</ref>，此舰是第九艘以「厄科」命名的船舰。

== 设计 ==
厄科号与企业号是皇家海军首批配备了[[全回转推进器|全回转推进器]]的船舰。全回转推进器与船首推进器均可透过船舰的整合导航系统以[[摇杆|摇杆]]操控，居高灵活性。


== 职责 ==
厄科号与其姊妹船是設計作測量、調查水文地理用以支援潛艦或兩棲任務之用。她可以向船艦提供近乎實時的客製化海域資訊，此外厄科号還可配備掃雷隊伍指揮作掃雷作業平台之用。<ref name=NN>{{cite web |url=http://www.navynews.co.uk/ships/echo.asp |title=''Echoes of a varied history'' – HMS Echo, ship of the month |date=May 2004 |publisher=Navy News |accessdate=2009-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080719190122/http://www.navynews.co.uk/ships/echo.asp |archive-date=2008-07-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

== 船員配置 ==
厄科号以三組專屬船員輪替作業，總作業人員數共72名，艦隻在任何情況下至少有三分之二船員維持運作。每個工作週期為75日，緊接是30日的休假供船員充分休息，而艦隻則可以在母港以外地方停留整備，通常每年一次。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.mod.uk/DefenceInternet/DefenceNews/TrainingAndAdventure/HmsEchoVisitsIndonesia.htm |title= HMS ''Echo'' visits Indonesia at Defence News |accessdate= 2009-06-20 |archive-date= 2009-03-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20090311022848/http://www.mod.uk/DefenceInternet/DefenceNews/TrainingAndAdventure/HmsEchoVisitsIndonesia.htm |dead-url= no }}</ref>

== 部署历史 ==
厄科号在2002年3月2日下水，3月4日由肯尼斯夫人<small>，海务大臣[[保罗・肯尼斯|保罗・肯尼斯]]（Sir Paul Haddacks）之妻</small>为其命名<ref name=RN/>。
及后在2002年10月4日获皇家海军驗収，2003年3月7日正式服役<ref name=RN/>。

=== 2004–2005：部署波斯湾 ===
厄科号在2004年编配至波斯湾进行测量任务，于2005年4月返回英国。<ref name=NN/>

=== 2008–2012：部署远东 ===
[[File:H87_ECHO.jpg|thumb]]卡尔卡拉]]
充分地利用她的人事輪替系統，厄科号部署至遠東進行海洋調查和外交訪問，為期五年。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-16231959.html |title=HMS ''Echo'' sets sail on five-year mission |publisher=Highbeam Research |accessdate=2009-06-20 }}{{Dead link|date=2019年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

2008年8月，厄科号停靠香港，指揮官在赤柱國殤紀念墳場向戰爭死難者獻上花圈。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.royalnavy.mod.uk/operations-and-support/surface-fleet/hydrographic-vessels/multi-role-survey-vessels/hms-echo/news/hms-echo-visit-to-hong-kong |title=HMS ''Echo'' visit to Hong Kong at the Royal Navy website |accessdate=2009-06-20 |language=en |archive-date=2009-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090504174016/http://www.royalnavy.mod.uk/operations-and-support/surface-fleet/hydrographic-vessels/multi-role-survey-vessels/hms-echo/news/hms-echo-visit-to-hong-kong |dead-url=no }}</ref>同年10月，她前往韓國[[釜山|釜山]]參與為慶祝韓國海軍建立60周年的國際艦隊檢閱活動。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.royalnavy.mod.uk/operations-and-support/surface-fleet/hydrographic-vessels/multi-role-survey-vessels/hms-echo/news/hms-echo-attends-international-fleet-review |title= HMS ''Echo'' Attends International Fleet Review – Busan, Republic of Korea at the Royal Navy website |accessdate= 2009-06-20 |language= en |archive-date= 2009-08-07 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20090807132144/http://www.royalnavy.mod.uk/operations-and-support/surface-fleet/hydrographic-vessels/multi-role-survey-vessels/hms-echo/news/hms-echo-attends-international-fleet-review |dead-url= no }}</ref>另還訪問孟加拉、馬來西亞、新加坡、汶萊和印尼等南海諸國進行交流。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.royalnavy.mod.uk/operations-and-support/surface-fleet/hydrographic-vessels/multi-role-survey-vessels/hms-echo/news/echo-gets-wet-n-wild-in |title=''Echo'' Gets Wet N' Wild In the South China Sea at the Royal Navy website |accessdate=2009-06-20 |language=en |archive-date=2009-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091207204032/http://www.royalnavy.mod.uk/operations-and-support/surface-fleet/hydrographic-vessels/multi-role-survey-vessels/hms-echo/news/echo-gets-wet-n-wild-in |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2012年2月，厄科号訪問[[塞舌爾|塞舌爾]]協助訓練當地海岸防衞機關，當中包括停靠首都[[維多利亞_(塞席爾)|維多利亞]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://navynews.co.uk/archive/news/item/3641 |date=2012-02-14 |title=Echo joins the fight against piracy in the Seychelles |work=Navy News |publisher=[[Royal_Navy|Royal Navy]] |accessdate= |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131225002029/https://navynews.co.uk/archive/news/item/3641 |archive-date=2013-12-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>8月16日返回母港德雲港，遠東任務歷時將近一年半，途中也有參與打擊[[索馬里海盜|索馬里海盜]]的[[聯合保安行動|聯合保安行動]]。

=== 2013年7月：部署地中海 ===
2013年7月，厄科号在地中海中部近[[的黎波里|的黎波里]]、[[胡姆斯|胡姆斯]]等港口一带測繪，以提昇有關[[利比亞|利比亞]]沿岸[[海圖|海圖]]資訊之精度。同時厄科号亦致力於搜尋可能影響航道安全的障礙物。在10日間發現一艘貨輪、兩艘商船、兩艘漁船、兩艘駁船、兩艘大型躉船及一般登陸艦的殘骸，另外也尋獲不少的遺失貨櫃。而發現的登陸艇遺骸則相信是屬於[[利比亞海軍|利比亞海軍]]的[[北方級登陸艦|北方級登陸艦]]（Polnocny）「''Ibn Qis''」，在1978年的軍演中遭焚毀。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gov.uk/government/news/hms-echo-finds-18-wrecks-off-libya |title=HMS Echo finds 18 wrecks off Libya |publisher=[[Ministry_of_Defence_(United_Kingdom)|Ministry of Defence]] |date=25 July 2013 |accessdate=2013-08-20 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111230506/https://www.gov.uk/government/news/hms-echo-finds-18-wrecks-off-libya |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.issconline.com/article.php?id=18601 |title=厄科号发现18艘船舶残骸 |access-date=2014-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130917130543/http://issconline.com/article.php?id=18601 |archive-date=2013-09-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

=== 2014年3月：部署印度洋 ===
2014年3月20日[[英國國防部|英國國防部]]受澳洲當局邀約，厄科号奉命從[[波斯灣|波斯灣]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.itv.com/news/update/2014-03-20/uk-sending-hms-echo-to-assist-in-malaysia-plane-search/ |title=ITV News item, 20 March 2014 |access-date=2014-03-24 |archive-date=2019-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190729114803/https://www.itv.com/news/update/2014-03-20/uk-sending-hms-echo-to-assist-in-malaysia-plane-search/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>調派至[[澳洲|澳洲]][[珀斯|珀斯]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/malaysia/10713312/Malaysian-Airlines-MH370-March-20-as-it-happened.html |title=Daily Telegraph ''(retrieved 21 March 2012)'' |access-date=2014-03-24 |archive-date=2019-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190729114802/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/malaysia/10713312/Malaysian-Airlines-MH370-March-20-as-it-happened.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>西南面約{{convert|2400|km|mi}}處參與搜索[[馬來西亞航空370號班機空難|馬航MH370航班]]。按原定計劃，厄科号會在波斯灣進行水文測量工作直至獲令返回英國。

在此三日前（3月17日），澳洲政府同意負責搜尋失蹤客機可能航行的南面路線，由印尼[[蘇門答臘|蘇門答臘]]遠至印度洋南面偏遠地區。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thestar.com.my/News/Nation/2014/03/17/Missing-MH370-Australia/|title=Missing MH370: Australia to lead southern search for MH370|work=The Star|date=2014-03-17|language=en|accessdate=2014-03-24|archive-date=2020-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417054118/https://www.thestar.com.my/News/Nation/2014/03/17/Missing-MH370-Australia/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.canberratimes.com.au/federal-politics/political-news/australia-agrees-to-lead-search-in-indian-ocean-for-missing-malaysia-airlines-flight-mh370-20140317-34xay.html|title=Australia agrees to lead search in Indian Ocean for missing Malaysia Airlines flight MH370|work=The Canberra Times|date=2014-03-17|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517130658/http://www.canberratimes.com.au/federal-politics/political-news/australia-agrees-to-lead-search-in-indian-ocean-for-missing-malaysia-airlines-flight-mh370-20140317-34xay.html|archivedate=2014-05-17|df=|accessdate=2014-03-24}}</ref>搜索行動由澳洲海事安全局主導，在介於珀斯{{convert|3000|km}}處至[[凱爾蓋朗群島|凱爾蓋朗群島]]總共約{{convert|600000|sqkm|sqmi}}的劃定範圍搜尋，澳洲、紐西蘭、美國軍方均有派遣資源協助。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2014-03-18/australia-takes-charge-of-multinational-search/5328904|title=Malaysia Airlines MH370: AMSA to coordinate new search 3,000 kilometres south-west of Perth|publisher=ABC News|date=2014-03-18|language=en|accessdate=2014-03-24|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117102852/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2014-03-18/australia-takes-charge-of-multinational-search/5328904|dead-url=no}}</ref>

